org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.view.model
Interface DynNetworkView<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Known Implementing Classes:
DynNetworkViewImpl
public interface DynNetworkView<T>

DynNetworkView is an object that represents a the view of a dynamic network. It provides the link to the current static DynNetwork.

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
